    "Id": "chassisdef_megalodon_MLDN-A",
    "Name": "Megalodon",
    "Details": "The A configuration saturates targets with coordinated missile fire. Twin ATM 12s with full ER, standard and HE ammunition loads cover every engagement range while a Streak LRM 20 adds guaranteed long-range damage. Fixed Medium Pulse Lasers ensure the design remains dangerous even after missile stocks run low. CASE II protects all four ammunition bays from catastrophic detonation.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Combat Computer</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.19</color></b>",
