  "StockRole": "Brawler",
  "YangsThoughts": "Clan Sea Fox built this a few years before Clan Wolf took Terra, named it after their old Diamond Shark identity. It sold well. The Federated Suns, Lyran Commonwealth, Capellans, Taurian Concordat, even the Magistracy bought their own versions. Hell's Horses ran a few variants too. Three hard-wired Medium Pulse Lasers in the left torso no matter what config you drop in, which tells you exactly how Sea Fox wanted this thing used. They built it to sell, and they built it right.",
